quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  46,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  46,1,Haa-Meeem
  46,2,( yeh ) kitaab khuday-e ghalib ( aur ) hikmat walay ki taraf se nazil hui hai
  46,3,hum ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un dono mein hai mabni bar hikmat aur aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye pedakiya hai. aur kafiroon ko jis cheez ki nasiyaat ki jati hai is se munh phair letay hain
  46,4,kaho ke bhala tum ne un cheezon ko dekha hai jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho ( zara ) mujhe bhi to dikhao ke unhon ne zameen mein kon si cheez peda ki hai. ya asmano mein un ki shirkat hai. agar sachey ho to is se pehlay ki koi kitaab mere paas lao. ya ilm ( anbia mein ) se kuch ( manqool ) chala aata ho ( to usay paish karo )
  46,5,aur is shakhs se barh kar kon gumraah ho sakta hai jo aisay ko pukare jo qayamat taq usay jawab nah day sakay aur un ko un ke pukarnay hi ki khabar nah ho
  46,6,aur jab log jama kiye jayen ge to woh un ke dushman hon ge aur un ki parastish se inkaar karen ge
  46,7,aur jab un ke samnay hamari khuli ayatain parhi jati hain to kafir haq ke baray mein jab un ke paas aachuka kehte hain ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
  46,8,kiya yeh kehte hain ke is ne is ko az khud bana liya hai. keh do ke agar mein ne is ko apni taraf se banaya ho to tum khuda ke samnay mere ( bachao ke ) liye kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay. woh is guftagu ko khoob jaanta hai jo tum is ke baray mein karte ho. wohi mere aur tumahray darmain gawah kaafi hai. aur woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  46,9,keh do ke mein koi naya paighambar nahi aaya. aur mein nahi jaanta ke mere sathkiya sulooqkiya jaye ga aur tumahray sathkiya (kiya jaye ga ) mein to isi ki pairwi karta hon jo mujh par wahi aati hai aur mera kaam to alania hadaayat karna hai
  46,10,kaho ke bhala dekho to agar yeh ( quran ) khuda ki taraf se ho aur tum ne is se inkaarkiya aur bani Israel mein se aik gawah isi terhan ki aik ( kitaab ) ki gawahi day chuka aur imaan le aaya aur tum ne sar kashi ki ( to tumahray zalim honay meinkiya shak hai ). be shak khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  46,11,aur kafir mominoun se kehte hain ke agar yeh ( deen ) kuch behtar hota to yeh log is ki taraf hum se pehlay nah daud parte aur jab woh is se hadaayat yab nah hue to ab kahin ge ke yeh purana jhoot hai
  46,12,aur is se pehlay moose ki kitaab thi ( logon ke liye ) rehnuma aur rehmat. aur yeh kitaab arabi zabaan mein hai isi ki tasdeeq karne wali taakay zaalmon ko dry. aur naiko karon ko khushkhabri sunaye
  46,13,jin logon ne kaha ke hamara perwar-digaar khuda hai phir woh ( is par ) qaim rahay to un ko nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  46,14,yahi ahal jannat hain ke hamesha is mein rahen ge. ( yeh ) is ka badla ( hai ) jo wohkiya karte they
  46,15,aur hum ne ensaan ko apne walidain ke sath bhalai karne ka hukum diya. is ki maa ne is ko takleef se pait mein rakha aur takleef hi se jina. aur is ka pait mein rehna aur doodh chhorna dhai baras mein hota hai. yahan taq ke jab khoob jawan hota hai aur chalees baras ko poanch jata hai to kehta hai ke ae mere perwar-digaar mujhe tofeq day ke to ne jo ahsaan mujh par aur mere maa baap par kiye hain un ka shukar guzaar hon aur yeh ke naik amal karoon jin ko to pasand kere. aur mere liye meri aulaad mein isalah ( o taqwa ) de. mein teri taraf rujoo karta hon aur mein farma- bardaron mein hon
  46,16,yahi log hain jin ke aamaal naik hum qubool karen ge aur un ke gunaaho se dar guzar farmaen ge aur ( yahi ) ahal jannat mein ( hon ge ). ( yeh ) sacha wada ( hai ) jo un sekiya jata hai
  46,17,aur jis shakhs ne apne maa baap se kaha ke uff uff! tum mujhe yeh batatay ho ke mein ( zameen se ) nikala jaoon ga halaank bohat se log mujh se pehlay guzar chuke hain. aur woh dono khuda ki janab mein faryaad karte ( hue kehte ) they ke kam bakht imaan laa. khuda ka wada to sacha hai. to kehnay laga yeh to pehlay logon ki kahaniyan hain
  46,18,yahi woh log hain jin ke baray mein junoo aur insanon ki ( doosri ) amtoN mein se jo un se pehlay guzar chakain azaab ka wada tehqeeq hogaya. be shak woh nuqsaan uthany walay they
  46,19,aur logon ne jaisay kaam kiye hon ge un ke mutabiq sab ke darjay hon ge. gharz yeh hai ke un ko un ke aamaal ka poora badla day aur un ka nuqsaan nahkiya jaye
  46,20,"aur jis din kafir dozakh ke samnay kiye jayen ge ( to kaha jaye ga ke ) tum apni duniya ki zindagi mein lazite haasil kar chukay aur un se mtmta ho chukay so aaj tum ko zillat ka azaab hai, ( yeh ) is ki saza ( hai ) ke tum zameen mein na-haq ghuroorkiya karte they. aur is ki bud-kardari karte they"
  46,21,aur ( qoum ) Aad ke bhai ( Hood ) ko yaad karo ke jab unhon ne apni qoum ko sarzamen ahqaaf mein hadaayat ki aur un se pehlay aur peechay bhi hadaayat karne walay gzrchke they ke khuda ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karo. mujhe tumahray baray mein barray din ke azaab ka dar lagta hai
  46,22,kehnay lageykiya tum hamaray paas is liye aeye ho ke hum ko hamaray mabodon se phair do. agar sachey ho to jis cheez se hamein darate ho usay hum par le aao
  46,23,( unhon ne ) kaha ke ( is ka ) ilm to khuda hi ko hai. aur mein to jo ( ehkaam ) day kar bheja gaya hon woh tumhe pouncha raha hon lekin mein daikhta hon ke tum log nadani mein phas rahay ho
  46,24,phir jab unhon ne is ( azaab ko ) dekha ke baadal ( ki soorat mein ) un ke mahdanon ki taraf araha hai to kehnay lagey yeh to baadal hai jo hum par baras kar rahay ga. ( nahi ) balkay ( yeh ) woh cheez hai jis ke liye tum jaldi karte they yani aandhi jis mein dard dainay wala azaab bhara howa hai
  46,25,har cheez ko apne perwar-digaar ke hukum se tabah kiye deti hai to woh aisay hogaye ke un ke gharon ke siwa kuch nazar hi nahi aata tha. gunehgaar logon ko hum isi terhan saza diya karte hain
  46,26,aur hum ne un ko aisay Maqdoor diye they jo tum logon ko nahi diye aur inhen kaan aur ankhen aur dil diye they. to jab ke woh khuda ki aayton se inkaar karte they to nah to un ke kaan hi un ke kuch kaam aasakay aur nah ankhen aur nah dil. aur jis cheez seistehzaakiya karte they is ne un ko aa ghaira
  46,27,aur tumahray ird gird ki bustiyon ko hum ne halaak kar diya. aur baar baar ( apni ) nishanain zahir kar dein taakay woh rujoo karen
  46,28,to jin ko un logon ne taqarab ( khuda ) ke siwa mabood banaya tha unhon ne un ki kyun madad nah ki. balkay woh un ( ke samnay ) se gum hogaye. aur yeh un ka jhoot tha aur yahi woh iftirakiya karte they
  46,29,aur jab hum ne junoo mein se kayi shakhs tumhari taraf mutwajjah kiye ke quran sunen. to jab woh is ke paas aeye to ( aapas mein ) kehnay lagey ke khamosh raho. jab ( parhna ) tamam howa to apni baradri ke logon mein wapas gay ke ( un ko ) nasiyaat karen
  46,30,kehnay lagey ke ae qoum! hum ne aik kitaab suni hai jo moose ke baad nazil hui hai. jo ( kitaaben ) is se pehlay ( nazil hui ) hain un ki tasdeeq karti hai ( aur ) sacha ( deen ) aur seedha rasta batati hai
  46,31,ae qoum! khuda ki taraf bulanay walay ki baat qubool karo aur is par imaan lao. khuda tumahray gunah bakhash day ga aur tumhe dukh dainay walay azaab se panah mein rakhay ga
  46,32,aur jo shakhs khuda ki taraf bulanay walay ki baat qubool nah kere ga to woh zameen mein ( khuda ko ) aajiz nahi kar sakay ga aur nah is ke siwa is ke himayati hon ge. yeh log Sarih gumraahi mein hain
  46,33,kiya unhon ne nahi samgha ke jis khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya aur un ke peda karne se thaka nahi. woh is ( baat ) par bhi Qadir hai ke mardon ko zindah kar day. haan haan woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  46,34,aur jis roz aag ke samnay kiye jayen ge ( aur kaha jaye ga )kiya yeh haq nahi hai? to kahin ge kyun nahi hamaray perwar-digaar ki qasam ( haq hai ) hukum hoga ke tum jo ( duniya mein ) inkaarkiya karte they ( ab ) azaab ke mazay chako
  46,35,pas ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jis terhan aur aliiiii himmat paighambar sabr karte rahay hain isi terhan tum bhi sabr karo aur un ke liye ( azaab ) jaldi nah mango. jis din yeh is cheez ko dekhen ge jis ka un se wadakiya jata hai to ( khayaal karen ge ke ) goya ( duniya mein ) rahay hi nah they magar gharri bhar din. ( yeh quran ) pegham hai. so ( ab ) wohi halaak hon ge jo nafarman they
